| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2597 — Recovery Inhibition (bianlian)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 651a37d8-2827-5ebc-ac45-fd4bbeae6abd"
